						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Secretariat-of-the-Pacific-Community-Land-Resources-Department-August-Newsletter" title="Secretariat of the Pacific Community Land Resources Department August Newsletter " alt="link">Secretariat of the Pacific Community Land Resources Department August Newsletter </a></h2>

	
					<p><a href="http://www.spc.int/lrd/index.php?option=com_docman&amp;task=doc_download&amp;gid=1534&amp;Itemid=138" target="_self">In this edition</a> of the SPC LRD Newsletter, a number of new agricultural projects and their coordination effort are presented: the ACIAR’s Pacific Agribusiness Research and Development Initiative (PARDI), AusAID Pacific Horticultural and Agricultural Market Access (PHAMA) project; the FAO-IFAD Food Security and Sustainable Livelihoods Project (FSSLP); AusAID’s Enterprise Challenge Fund (ECF) and Market Development Facility (MDF); and the new EU-funded Increasing Agricultural Commodity Trade (IACT) and Agriculture and Rural Development (ARD) projects, and the Food Animal Biosecurity Network (FABN) project, among others. Also, one will find discussions on the improvement of the Pacific market information system, clean seed system for export taro, ag ministerial meeting, and SPC-INEA partnership on biotechnology.</p>
							<p><span class="date">12/01/2012</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Secretariat-of-the-Pacific-Community-Land-Resources-Department-August-Newsletter">Read more...</a>
</div>
<br class="cl">
